  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"node__content\"> <section class=\"detail-page-head full-width-block\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-12\"> <small>Antares Capital- <span class=\"field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden\"><time class=\"datetime\" datetime=\"2024-06-25T16:55:10+00:00\" title=\"Tuesday, June 25, 2024 - 16:55\">Tue, 06/25/2024 - 16:55</time></span></small><h1><span class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden\">Navigating private debt and capturing relative value in today's environment</span></h1></div></div></div> </section> <section class=\"detail-page additional-height\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-8-lg\"><div class=\"feature-image-visability\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-banner field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default insurance-library-image\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"><div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div><div class=\"field__item\"> <img alt=\"Antares\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid\" data-src=\"/sites/default/files/2024-06/Featured_16.jpg\" height=\"381\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2024-06/Featured_16.jpg\" width=\"908\"/></div></div> </article></div></div><div class=\"audio-player\"></div><table class=\"table\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:80%;\"></td><td><p>Delving into the current dynamics and future prospects of <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=privatedebt&amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7196179584118071296\">private </a>debt, Vivek Mathew, Antares’ Head of Asset Management, discusses what he believes to be the continued opportunity set for investors in the middle market in this interview with <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/private-debt-investor/\">Private Debt Inves